.121569 .160784 .215686 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 43.3 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 13.2 TL (Exact mathematical optimization formulations exist, but the search space grows quickly as jobs and machines) Tj T* (increase. This makes JSSP a useful setting for metaheuristics. ACO converts scheduling into repeated constructive) Tj T* (search: ants build sequences, good sequences receive more pheromone, and future ants are biased toward choices) Tj T* (that historically produced shorter schedules.) Tj T* ET
